rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0001
rows.name:
Now we can finally head
to the Superbian Empire.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0002
rows.name:
Quite the strenuous detour
we ended up taking there.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0003
rows.name:
I bet Masterpon has already forgotten
where we're supposed to board the ship.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0004
rows.name:
Let me think...
Was it the 10th floor?

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0005
rows.name:
Goldmund doesn't have
nearly that many floors!

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0006
rows.name:
It's on the 4th floor.
The Goldmund Flight Deck.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0007
rows.name: Come on, let's get a move on.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0008
rows.name:
Rex...
Make sure you keep
an eye on your things.
